    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Austrocarabodes nortoni sp. nov. holotype male, A. Dorsal view (100 μm). Magnifications of sensillus (ss), lamellar seta (le), notogastral seta da (50 μm); B: ventral view (100 μm)." ;
